Description: utilities for manipulating text files
 GNU gawk is a set of utilities used for manipulating text
 files. 

Package: gawk-dev
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), gawk (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Development API for GNU awk
 This package provides the header file gawkapi.h, which
 contains the gawk API.

Package: gawk-doc
